# Screener.in session cookie (works with Google / Gmail login)
#
# HOW TO GET YOUR SESSION ID (one-time setup, repeat if it expires):
#
#   1. Open Chrome or Edge and log in to https://www.screener.in
#   2. Press F12 to open DevTools
#   3. Go to: Application tab -> Cookies -> https://www.screener.in
#   4. Find the row where Name = "sessionid"
#   5. Copy the entire Value string
#   6. Paste it below (replace the placeholder)
#
# Session cookies typically last 2-4 weeks before expiring.
# If the script says "Session expired", repeat the steps above.

SCREENER_SESSION_ID=erbt6xgb67a7sax1im5iiu8aoj92s3q9
